{"tid":1834313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京呼籲安理會常任理事國保全球穩定　指俄國願與有志者共同維持和平 強調俄國不會威脅他人 從不強加自己意願於人上","createTime":"2020-01-22T10:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T19:54:37.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdaafcd26874e96104c0fb44e214f5008696b7d7","tid":1834313,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503032-20200116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503032-20200116.htm&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=0d965732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503032-20200116.htm&h=b308d024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503032-20200116.htm</a><br />\n俄羅斯總統普京發表國情咨文，在外交方面，他呼籲聯合國安理會五個常任理事國，致力保持全球穩定，又強調俄羅斯不會威脅任何國家。<br />\n<br />\n普京說，近期中東及北非局勢，出現難以預料的變化，地區衝突對國際社會構成威脅，有關各方需意識到有共同責任，採取實際行動，商討穩定世界秩序的基本原則。<br />\n<br />\n普京認為五個安理會常任理事國，必須採取措施，消除引發大戰的因素，保持世界穩定，俄羅斯願意與擁有相關意願的所有夥伴，加強合作。他強調俄羅斯不威脅任何國家，不會將自己的意願強加於人。"},{"pid":"975958a69e45a24c866fb3f11a7265bcc8d5c9d5","tid":1834313,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb9a4d770655048016b6d992b27c76a75635d19","tid":1834313,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1601f2e0a2ca81abcf55573dc77225334ff01b70","tid":1834313,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"有骨wor<br />\n串中國成日強加意願落人度"},{"pid":"beacbd0bc83e752034fa0819e4684105dc706462","tid":1834313,"uid":172668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"如果企係